.TH "nci_spi_allocate_spi" 9 "nci_spi_allocate_spi" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nci_spi_allocate_spi \- allocate a new nci spi
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct nci_spi *" nci_spi_allocate_spi
.BI "(struct spi_device *spi "  ","
.BI "u8 acknowledge_mode "  ","
.BI "unsigned int delay "  ","
.BI "struct nci_dev *ndev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "spi" 12
SPI device
.IP "acknowledge_mode" 12
Acknowledge mode used by the NFC device
.IP "delay" 12
delay between transactions in us
.IP "ndev" 12
nci dev to send incoming nci frames to
